author: Ben Kesslen
title: As Florida coronavirus cases surge, spring breakers express regret
description: As the U.S. is at about 55,000 cases of the virus, including more than 780 deaths, Brady Sluder has revised his message: “Don’t be arrogant and think you’re invincible like myself.”
content:
The clip went viral. If I get corona, I get corona. At the end of the day, Im not gonna let it stop me from partying, Brady Sluder, a spring breaker in Miami, said last week.
